org.cpsolver.studentsct.model

Class FreeTimeRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cpsolver.ifs.model.Variable<V,T>
      • org.cpsolver.ifs.assignment.context.VariableWithContext<Request,Enrollment,Request.RequestContext>
        • org.cpsolver.studentsct.model.Request
          • org.cpsolver.studentsct.model.FreeTimeRequest
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<Request>, CanHoldContext, HasAssignmentContext<Request,Enrollment,Request.RequestContext>, SctAssignment

    public class FreeTimeRequest
extends Request
implements SctAssignment
    Representation of a request of a student for free time. This class directly implements SctAssignment API, with the appropriate free time.

    Version:
    StudentSct 1.3 (Student Sectioning)
